text: Leo Burney (born November 2, 2001) is an American soccer player who plays for the Seattle Sounders FC academy. ==Career== Burney joined the Seattle Sounders FC academy in 2015. He made his debut for USL club Seattle Sounders FC 2 in August 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:American soccer players Category:Tacoma Defiance players Category:Association football midfielders Category:Soccer players from Washington (state) Category:USL Championship players Category:People from Tukwila, Washington
